request.description:
**Track order shipment status from Shiprocket.**

### Response:
```json
{
  "shipments": [{
    "warehouseId": "...",
    "provider": "Delhivery",
    "trackingNumber": "SR123456789",
    "labelUrl": "https://shiprocket.com/label.pdf",
    "trackUrl": "https://shiprocket.co.in/tracking/SR123456789",
    "trackingData": {
      "trackStatus": "delivered",
      "currentStatus": "...",
      "statusSteps": [...],
      "eta": "..."
    }
  }]
}
```

**Note:** `labelUrl` is the printable shipping label - open in browser to print.

